    The tests are based on actual events reported by SDL3.

    Co-authored-by: Bartłomiej Dach <dach.bartlomiej@gmail.com>
---
 .../Visual/UserInterface/TestSceneTextBoxEvents.cs | 116 +++++++++++++++++++++
