Author: Susko3 <Susko3@protonmail.com>
Date:   Sun Jan 5 00:35:01 2025 +0000

    Add proper SDL3 pen handling
---
 osu.Framework/Input/Handlers/Pen/PenHandler.cs  | 78 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 osu.Framework/Platform/SDL3/SDL3Window_Input.cs | 28 +++++++++
